paragraphs.title: Sales by Product Departments
paragraphs.text:
%mysql

select 
    d.department_name, count(distinct oi.order_item_order_id) no_of_orders, round(sum(oi.order_item_subtotal),2) total_sales, sum(oi.order_item_quantity) total_sold_qty
from 
    departments d
        join categories c on (d.department_id = c.category_department_id)
        join products p on (c.category_id = p.product_category_id) 
        join order_items oi on (p.product_id = oi.order_item_product_id)
group by d.department_name 
order by total_sales desc;

paragraphs.title: How did the Top-N selling Products in 2014 perform the previous year?
paragraphs.text:
%mysql

select 
    products.product_name, year(orders.order_date) order_year, round(sum(order_items.order_item_subtotal)) total_sales
from 
    products products
    join (select 
            p.product_id, round(sum(oi.order_item_subtotal),2) total_sales
        from 
            products p
                join order_items oi on (p.product_id = oi.order_item_product_id)
                join orders o on (oi.order_item_order_id = o.order_id)
        where 
            year(o.order_date) = 2014
        group by p.product_id 
        order by total_sales desc
        limit ${TopN=5,5|10|15|20}) topn_products on (products.product_id = topn_products.product_id)
    join order_items order_items on (products.product_id = order_items.order_item_product_id)
    join orders orders on (order_items.order_item_order_id = orders.order_id)
group by products.product_name, year(orders.order_date);

paragraphs.title: Top 10 Customers with Most Unique Product Purchases
paragraphs.text:
%mysql

select 
    c.customer_fname, count(distinct(oi.order_item_product_id)) unique_products, round(sum(oi.order_item_subtotal),2) total_sales, count(distinct o.order_id) no_of_orders, round(sum(oi.order_item_subtotal)/count(distinct o.order_id),2) avg_order_price
from
    customers c   
    inner join orders o on o.order_customer_id = c.customer_id  
    inner join order_items oi on o.order_id = oi.order_item_order_id  
group by c.customer_id, c.customer_fname  
order by unique_products desc, total_sales desc   
limit 10

paragraphs.title: Which State Customers mostly buy the products?
paragraphs.text:
%mysql

select
    c.customer_state, sum(oi.order_item_subtotal) total_sales
from 
    customers c
    join orders o on (c.customer_id = o.order_customer_id)
    join order_items oi on (o.order_id = oi.order_item_order_id)
group by c.customer_state
order by total_sales desc
